nodes.text: A Momong resided on the planet of Zygerria during the time of the Clone Wars.

Around 21 BBY, when Jedi Master Obi-Wan Kenobi along with Jedi Knight Anakin Skywalker, Padawan Ahsoka Tano and clone trooper captain Rex arrived on the planet to infiltrate the Zygerrian slave empire, this Momong was present in a slave market, dueling with a Kowakian monkey-lizard with miniature swords.
This Momong first appeared in the twelfth episode of the Star Wars: The Clone Wars television series' fourth season, titled "Slaves of the Republic".
